CSS :  Cascading Stylesheet :  

CSS are used for to design a web page :  

----------------------------------------

Types of css :  
1. External css : it create outsite the program 

<head>
    <link href="css file name" rel="stylesheet">
</head>

---------------------------------------------------

2.  Internal CSS  : it create inside the program(file)
<head>
    <style>
        css code here 
    </style>
</head>

------------------------------------------------

3. Inline CSS : It appy on every html tags  .. 

<h1 style="css code"></h1>
----------------------------------------------







3. Inline CSS 